intent.user_query: What is the total revenue generated by each product brand, and what percentage of total revenue does each brand represent?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.Brand, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS BrandRevenue, (SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) / (SELECT SUM(Quantity * UnitPrice) FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails)) * 100 AS PercentageOfTotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY BrandRevenue DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.Brand, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS BrandRevenue, (SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) / (SELECT SUM(Quantity * UnitPrice) FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails)) * 100 AS PercentageOfTotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY BrandRevenue DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
